    "description": "<strong>你进入了一个阈限和怀旧的世界。泳池屋宁静的蓝水和干净的瓷砖带给人梦幻般的感觉。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2>Poolcore 是一款第一人称行走模拟器，玩家在此穿越梦幻般的泳池屋。你掉入了这个世界，现在必须观察这些古老的水和墙是否有可感知的特征。探索并解决谜题，取得游戏进展。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>逼真的图像。<br></li><li>手工制作的大型关卡。<br></li><li>轻柔的音乐。<br></li><li>独特的谜题。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251780/extras/9135d1b2d234042903244646a15a01fe.poster.avif?t=1763050229\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251780/extras/9135d1b2d234042903244646a15a01fe.webm?t=1763050229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251780/extras/9135d1b2d234042903244646a15a01fe.mp4?t=1763050229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251780/extras/8931f428d36053232e5400d44d788cb4.poster.avif?t=1763050229\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251780/extras/8931f428d36053232e5400d44d788cb4.webm?t=1763050229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251780/extras/8931f428d36053232e5400d44d788cb4.mp4?t=1763050229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>",
